{
  "stem": "27443.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "When I find David, I'll come back, and we'll stay in Lodz, all of us, together.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I boarded a train to Skarzysko, and I went back to Skarzysko.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And David's brother and an aunt who was liberated by Poles, an elderly woman, was liberated.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Met me by the train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I stayed by them a few days, by her aunt.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "By the aunt.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I stayed there a few days, till that fellow Srulek came back, was liberated, and told me the bad news, that David is no more alive.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And that day, I boarded a train back to Lodz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I arrived to Lodz, and I couldn't find my girlfriend anymore, because she went with another group out of Poland.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I boarded a train to [NON-ENGLISH] the same night, all by myself.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I went to [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "From [NON-ENGLISH], I went to [NON-ENGLISH], [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and to the border that was the Polish-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] between Czechoslovakia-- the border between Poland and Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I came to [NON-ENGLISH], and they arrested me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The Polish Army arrested me and put me back on a train back to Poland.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I started to cry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And at that time, I had an [NON-ENGLISH], a document.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "My name was-- from the concentration camp, my name was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And having that document, I started to cry, and they allowed me to go into the office.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Because with my Polish language, I came to the office, and I pretended that I am a Pole, not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said to them, what do you think, I'm a Polish citizen?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And do you think that I tried to run away from Poland?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is my country.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I am only going because I found out that my father is in Prague.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
